{"tid":452132,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"遊台BNO 與 特衰護照問題","createTime":"2017-10-30T01:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T07:15:33.000Z","uid":53643,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3a96b84065fa0d27e5463eb32461860f16a79b19","tid":452132,"uid":53643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:43:53.000Z","msg":"幾年前用過特衰去台灣，因為當時未續返本BNO，早排睇電視先知用過特衰就唔可以用BNO入境<br />\n有冇咩方法可以用BNO入境（我可以取消本特衰）"},{"pid":"0b5285a988a0a4c202131bcf81d34365e7abb444","tid":452132,"uid":133375,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:50:32.000Z","msg":"聽都未聽過用特衰就唔用得bno"},{"pid":"c07a6ca9ef415e44404f65d604ba022414b44031","tid":452132,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽都未聽過用特衰就唔用得bno</blockquote><br />\nx2"},{"pid":"497ccc7b0487c03ac24bab02441ae18374057103","tid":452132,"uid":59777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:55:06.000Z","msg":"入台灣<br />\n如果你有兩本護照(例如 特區及美國先算啦)<br />\n最好每次用同一本入"},{"pid":"30d6e2a6f4e243a75f55ecfddd3ea728606db024","tid":452132,"uid":53643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:58:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽都未聽過用特衰就唔用得bno</blockquote><br />\n我之前都未聽過，係早排睇電視訪問地勤，話有人到左台灣彈返轉頭，不過冇講明BNO同特衰，我剩係知台灣唔認可雙重國籍，有冇巴打試過用完特衰再用BNO入到境"},{"pid":"fc8667406826061e6069230f336e84903c178b66","tid":452132,"uid":77813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:01:22.000Z","msg":"Email 問過台灣移民署話得<br />\n但佢建議話唔好調轉用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者帶晒兩本有咩事做落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec019c2405d88026dd6e653a55ca688396024e2e","tid":452132,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽都未聽過用特衰就唔用得bno</blockquote><br />\nx2</blockquote><br />\nx3"},{"pid":"cfcc170fc166be340882df8dfe578a236407e45b","tid":452132,"uid":50554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:28:20.000Z","msg":"試過第一次去用特區<br />\n第二次去用bno關員問我係咪確定以後都用bno我話係<br />\n佢話入左system 如果下次用特區就會入唔到境"},{"pid":"e7f0050a8466f9e71ffd1c9827c99d041d1663e7","tid":452132,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:19:19.000Z","msg":"係佢system只可以一個人一個國籍啫<br />\n冇話「唔可以」<br />\n你鍾意梅花間竹用兩本passport入都得㗎<br />\n只係佢每次都要update之嘛<br />\n當然佢都有懷疑你用假護照嘅權利<br />\n又或者彈你走<br />\n但台灣人邊夠膽玩咁大丫<br />\n台灣又想做發達國家<br />\n而發達國家就算唔認雙重國籍都好<br />\n好少會主動畀麻煩雙重國籍嘅人<br />\n而原因只係純粹係因為佢雙重國籍"},{"pid":"8d83ea805499acd9f3f7996c7fd90edd0674d8fa","tid":452132,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:29:28.000Z","msg":"7年前去用 CNO<br />\n今年去用 BNO<br />\n試過冇問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班台妹酒店 reception 見你係香港人但拎住本 BNO<br />\n即刻出晒水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">(<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">咁都出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> )<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"756abe8b2a38c54f18e9cbbe63ca18bb1880c2eb","tid":452132,"uid":92123,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7年前去用 CNO<br />\n今年去用 BNO<br />\n試過冇問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班台妹酒店 reception 見你係香港人但拎住本 BNO<br />\n即刻出晒水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">(<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">咁都出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> )<br />\n</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我check in 用bno d台妹一樣西西地面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">利申絲</span></span>"},{"pid":"d659d19cc8ae67f0d20186d3182503385f87caf0","tid":452132,"uid":92123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:51:15.000Z","msg":"回正題,<br />\n<br />\n用bno 冇問題, <br />\n你張入台證個passport no. 入番bno 個no. 就ok<br />\n上個月先去完, 第一次用bno入台"},{"pid":"3b79d944fda69c7843708d89c583202dd1f59584","tid":452132,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"我幾本都試過，完全冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBNO=&gt;特衰=&gt;Emergency Travel Documents=&gt;BNO<br />\n<br />\n其實佢主要睇你入台證。"},{"pid":"c0ea5bb9b855a1e3c43188b6ddd1728ca6627483","tid":452132,"uid":3937,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽都未聽過用特衰就唔用得bno</blockquote><br />\n我之前都未聽過，係早排睇電視訪問地勤，話有人到左台灣彈返轉頭，不過冇講明BNO同特衰，我剩係知台灣唔認可雙重國籍，有冇巴打試過用完特衰再用BNO入到境</blockquote><br />\n同事試過<br />\n不過佢係BC<br />\n<br />\n佢之前用BC入過台灣<br />\n前排用特區入被拒"},{"pid":"7a651aa5d4c2c96a3f7ab1b77aa8c5f9af49f3f8","tid":452132,"uid":53643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:24:40.000Z","msg":"有巴打試過ok就冇問題喇，我仲諗緊特衰到期好唔好去續"},{"pid":"42b3dc450c71a15494792f0785d3efeeb9bdd2b6","tid":452132,"uid":24296,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"我渣楓葉國passport以前入過台灣幾次<br />\n今年係uk  讀完書個陣順便歐遊<br />\n因為太掛住Asian food <br />\n所以返黎個陣買左飛台灣既機票 <br />\n打算停台灣幾日再飛香港<br />\n因為我個study  visa  整左係特區護照<br />\n我只係帶左HKSAR passport 無帶到Canada passport <br />\n結果到台灣  佢唔比入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ccececea08c0df2fa82708a022b1d98833272b9","tid":452132,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我渣楓葉國passport以前入過台灣幾次<br />\n今年係uk  讀完書個陣順便歐遊<br />\n因為太掛住Asian food <br />\n所以返黎個陣買左飛台灣既機票 <br />\n打算停台灣幾日再飛香港<br />\n因為我個study  visa  整左係特區護照<br />\n我只係帶左HKSAR passport 無帶到Canada passport <br />\n結果到台灣  佢唔比入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪冇入台證"},{"pid":"65f198a3baec655f169df9000a44f464cad16496","tid":452132,"uid":130543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:42:54.000Z","msg":"搭單問葡萄牙護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前用特衰入過<br />\n依家轉葡照<br />\n係咪淨係以後用唔返特衰入呢個副作用？<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badeb3912116e69a7ef8df2af7864497785a7a80","tid":452132,"uid":98172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:44:54.000Z","msg":"之前有新聞係香港人用過特衰, 再用BNO分台灣被拒入境<br />\n<br />\n但係我又咁做, 都可以順利入到"},{"pid":"46e61d605a26e6bbe0d5fffaf90f232ce92cd5c1","tid":452132,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:48:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽都未聽過用特衰就唔用得bno</blockquote><br />\n我之前都未聽過，係早排睇電視訪問地勤，話有人到左台灣彈返轉頭，不過冇講明BNO同特衰，我剩係知台灣唔認可雙重國籍，有冇巴打試過用完特衰再用BNO入到境</blockquote><br />\nTVB 個低能記者，屌"},{"pid":"07af65e2d0b99b900a573c66a5b6d6cccda259f9","tid":452132,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前有新聞係香港人用過特衰, 再用BNO分台灣被拒入境<br />\n<br />\n但係我又咁做, 都可以順利入到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單新聞係個白痴記者冇了解清楚，個人本護照係英國護照唔係bno"},{"pid":"6b998b1d73fbefa501b4d40952181d98d6593e31","tid":452132,"uid":38376,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:51:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽都未聽過用特衰就唔用得bno</blockquote><br />\n我之前都未聽過，係早排睇電視訪問地勤，話有人到左台灣彈返轉頭，不過冇講明BNO同特衰，我剩係知台灣唔認可雙重國籍，有冇巴打試過用完特衰再用BNO入到境</blockquote><br />\n同事試過<br />\n不過佢係BC<br />\n<br />\n佢之前用BC入過台灣<br />\n前排用特區入被拒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英國護照的話，的確係咁，如果你用英國護照入過，你就係英國人，點解仲要用中國護照入？"},{"pid":"9c320938d25c661eb21c0da5569d7adaeb022ed4","tid":452132,"uid":148734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"今年二月用特衰出入境<br />\n六月就用BNO<br />\n無事"},{"pid":"94bd65a00e5c8d455862f102988c0dc90f485f8e","tid":452132,"uid":38376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:52:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問葡萄牙護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前用特衰入過<br />\n依家轉葡照<br />\n係咪淨係以後用唔返特衰入呢個副作用？<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，你用葡萄牙護照入，即係你係葡萄牙人。點解仲要死痴住中國人個身分？貪支那領事館好服務，出事理得你？"},{"pid":"4299074d4b1e47df01420a76e44e25a3ee4a9948","tid":452132,"uid":130543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:01:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭單問葡萄牙護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前用特衰入過<br />\n依家轉葡照<br />\n係咪淨係以後用唔返特衰入呢個副作用？<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，你用葡萄牙護照入，即係你係葡萄牙人。點解仲要死痴住中國人個身分？貪支那領事館好服務，出事理得你？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無啊 我驚有其他副作用咋<br />\n完全唔想用CNO<br />\n之前細個唔識續就話用CNO姐<br />\n<br />\n無記錯仲有副作用就係台灣只認cno去台灣升學係香港人<br />\n<br />\n唔該曬巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特衰唔會再續<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}